* Task 2 fixture: Lexer token types
* This file contains minimal examples of each token type.

CALLNAT 'PROGRAM'           /* Keyword + string literal
PERFORM SUBROUTINE          /* Keyword + identifier
FETCH 'MYPROG'              /* Keyword + string literal
INCLUDE 'COPYBOOK'          /* Keyword + string literal
RUN PROGRAM                 /* Keyword + identifier

MOVE 12345 TO VAR           /* Numeric literal
MOVE 3.14159 TO PI          /* Decimal literal

IF X <> Y THEN              /* Operators
SET @VAR = 'value'          /* Punctuation

* This is a comment          * Comment

END                         /* EOF
